<m:mtext>C</m:mtext>
</m:math>? (c) What gravitational potential energy is gained by this volume of air if it rises 1.00 m? Will this cause a significant cooling of the air?</para></problem>
      <solution id="fs-id3201581">
      <para id="fs-id3127000">(a) 1.102</para>
        <para id="fs-id1579414">(b) <m:math>
